&kp QMARK  &kp TILDE  &kp LT    &kp MINUS  &kp GT     &kp SLASH  &kp LGUI   &kp LCTRL  &kp LALT  &trans  &trans  &trans  &none    &kp COLON  &kp LS(TAB)  &none      &none      &none
&none      &none      &kp LBRC  &kp RBRC   &kp PLUS              &kp PRCNT  &kp DOT    &kp SEMI  &trans  &trans  &trans           &kp LSHFT  &kp LCTRL    &kp LALT   &kp LGUI   &none
