&none          &none      &none      &none      &none      &none                                                        &none      &none      &kp STAR  &none   &none      &none
&none          &kp LBKT   &kp LPAR   &kp RPAR   &kp RBKT   &kp PERCENT                                                  &kp CARET  &kp N7     &kp N8    &kp N9  &kp MINUS  &none
&kp LG(ENTER)  &kp ENTER  &kp SPACE  &kp UP     &kp UNDER  &kp COMMA                                                    &kp EQUAL  &kp N4     &kp N5    &kp N6  &kp PLUS   &kp DQT
&none          &none      &kp LEFT   &kp DOWN   &kp RIGHT  &kp DOT      &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &kp N0     &kp N1     &kp N2    &kp N3  &kp FSLH   &none
&none          &kp LGUI   &kp LALT   &kp LCTRL  &kp LSHFT               &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans             &kp COLON  &kp LT    &kp GT  &none      &none
            >;
